simulation.simulation

Class Simulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • simulation.simulation.Simulator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Simulator
extends java.lang.Thread
    The Simulator simulates our system. It contains a Map and a set of MapComponent. It is executed on a different thread.
    Author:
    S.A.M. Janssen
